                            <div data-speed="1.2" style="max-width: 900px;">
                                <span
                                    style="color: #6F2BFF; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;">06
                                    /</span>
                                <h2
                                    style="font-family: var(--td-ff-heading), sans-serif; font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 90px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 30px 0; letter-spacing: -3px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6F2BFF 0%, #9B66FF 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">
                                    AI Agents<br>& Systems</h2>
                                <p
                                    style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px); line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 400; margin: 0; max-width: 600px;">
                                    Deploy autonomous AI agents that work for you 24/7. From customer support bots to
                                    complex operational systems, we build intelligent agents that scale your business
